{"tid":1421111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線休息，各區街坊應該一齊去差館報案，逼差佬作出交代。","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:37:36.000Z","uid":36797,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5f38dad6c0f2129812fba7ec0022671968330691","tid":1421111,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"將軍澳有阿伯行過比差佬打，打完又唔係拘捕；<br />\n黃大仙有老人家被差佬壓倒地上；<br />\n北角、荃灣有黑社會出黎斬人，有相有片；<br />\n天水圍強逼被捕少女當眾露下體。<br />\n<br />\n可能仲有地方漏左，呼籲各位喺各大街坊平台提出，約時間一齊去要求交代。<br />\n前線需要休息，但行動不能停止，我地出師有名，行得正企得正。"},{"pid":"53c0fe9eb853e231efe42bc6454df122438cbda4","tid":1421111,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa774462176979c9ce9e8a73d2ad3cdd10e5bc77","tid":1421111,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:12:12.000Z","msg":"無人做野呀？"},{"pid":"a48233c4a2cc8769ae9cfd1478595545effbc100","tid":1421111,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b70b46aa13df4d137e8ad615ebaba6230e1cc0","tid":1421111,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:35:25.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解琴晚又有黑底出黎呀?<br />\n因為我地想休息，差佬都想休息呀，街坊做野啦，唔好比佢地有氣透。<br />\n成日話和理非想做多啲野支持前線，做啦!!!!!"},{"pid":"704eb39d999fce554f4544882306063a7313b2bd","tid":1421111,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"放工肯做既留個言幫手推啦"},{"pid":"bf3a6ed7c6e05278102f5c8db33160539b6ff520","tid":1421111,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"收工做野啦"},{"pid":"f5e5608ae427fd366648b26df673bb54c89e2f61","tid":1421111,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:21:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">